items.badge_description: 99 bottles of beer on the wall, 99 bottles of beer. Take one down, pass it around.... That's 20 checkins with the serving style of Bottle. Try 5 more for Level 5!

Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 10 different venues categorized as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 3!

Hiking, fishing, swimming - there are so many wonderful things to do while you enjoy the great outdoors. Even beer is better when surrounded by the beauty of nature. That's 15 different venues categorized as Great Outdoors. Visit 5 more for Level 4!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 25 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 6!
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren't you?. That's 15 different Lagers! Try 5 more to unlock Level 4.

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 15 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 4!
Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 225 distinct venues!
Travel much? You must be a "brewsetter". That's at least a beer from 15 different countries. Try 5 more for Level 4!

The craft beer revolution is making it’s way South with micro brewed alternatives popping up throughout Central and South America! That's 5 different beers from a brewery from either Central or South America. Try 5 more for Level 2!
